  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Ghana Education Quality Improvement Project (EQUIP)</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Provision of high-quality core textbooks for English, Maths, Science and accompanying teacher guides for over 5.6 million school children in Ghana.  This is to ensure that quality education is improved and sustained at both primary and junior high school.  This contributes to our MDGs by providing essential  teaching and learning materials which will result in improved attendance and learning achievements by 2015.</narrative>
  </description>
